WEBVTT

00:01:58.546 --> 00:02:03.455
Ho'sh, qanday qilib bu yetkazib 
berishlarni kamaytirish mumkin?

00:02:04.661 --> 00:02:06.391
Bu savolga

00:02:06.415 --> 00:02:09.913
men va jamoam oxirgi uch yil davomida
javob qidiramiz.

00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:13.475
Uning yechimi esa, aslida
kelajak shahrining

00:02:13.499 --> 00:02:15.341
turar-joylaridan biridir,

00:02:15.944 --> 00:02:20.155
Biz o'zini boshqaradigan, kichik
robotlarni yaratib kelmoqdamiz.

00:02:20.179 --> 00:02:22.806
Ular hiyobon va piyodalar yo'laklarida
harakatlanadi,

00:02:22.830 --> 00:02:24.512
yurish tezligida

00:02:24.536 --> 00:02:28.106
va ishonchli yuk yetkazib berish 
qobiliyatiga ega.

00:02:28.130 --> 00:02:31.304
Robotlar haqida yana ma'lumot 
berishimdan oldin,